.TH "nvme_ctrl_get_attr" 9 "nvme_ctrl_get_attr" "March 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
nvme_ctrl_get_attr \- Read controller sysfs attribute
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "char *" nvme_ctrl_get_attr
.BI "(nvme_ctrl_t c "  ","
.BI "const char *attr "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "c" 12
Controller instance
.IP "attr" 12
sysfs attribute name
.SH "RETURN"
String with the contents of \fIattr\fP or NULL in case of an empty value
or in case of an error.
